window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In a galaxy tied together by the magic of the elite Jump Magi, Damien Montgomery is a newly graduated member of their number. With no family or connections to find a ship, he is forced into service on an interstellar freighter known to be hunted by pirates. When he takes drastic action to save the <i>Blue Jay</i> from their pursuers, he sets in motion a sequence of events beyond his control and attracts enemies on both sides of the law. </p>"; 
